mple developing move. Our plan is to push ...b4 next followed by ...a5 and maybe ...Ba6 to exchange the bishops. } 15. f5 b4 16. Nd1 a5 { It pays off to gain space. } 17. Nf2 Qb6 { The most precise. We can continue ...c4 or ...Ba6 next depending on what White does. } *

