ttention. } 16... Qa5 { With the idea to play ...Ba4. } 17. Qd4 Ba4 { This works nevertheless. The lines are very concrete. } 18. Bxf6 Bxf6 19. Qxf6 cxb2 20. Qxb2 Rc2 { Here we can see the idea of ...Ba4. Black is going to regain the material after } 21. Qd4 b3+ 22. Kf1 b2 23. Rd1 Nd7 { The idea is to go ...Rb8 next. } 24. g4 Rb8 25. Kg2 Rxe2 26. Nxe2 Bxd1 27. Rxd1 b1=Q 28. Rxb1 Rxb1 { With compensation. } *

