ion. } 16. Ng3 { This was played in 0-1 (29) Shankland,S (2602)-Gao,R  (2454) Santa Clara 2014. } 16... Nd7 ( { This is probably even stronger than Gao’s } 16... h5 { Black is on top. The knight comes to c5, further reinforcing the control over d3 and b3. } ) *

