17. Ncxd6 { This immediate capture fails. White cannot take the pawn yet. } 17... Bxb5 { After this the d3-bishop and d6-knight are loose pieces, and White will have to forfeit one of them. } 18. Bxb5 Bd4+ { The knight on d6 is lost. } *

