 of playing ...Bb5. } 19. Qb3 Bb5 { A good resource. We give back the pawn but exchange some pieces and open the a-file for our rook. } 20. Bxb5 axb5 21. Qxb5 Bf8 { It's important to keep the d6-pawn defended. } 22. Ng5 Na6 { With an equal game. } *

