ar cut than } 19... Bf8 { . Now the position will be clarified into an equal ending. } ) 20. Bxb5 Nc6 { The only move. } 21. Qxd5 Bb7 { Again, the only reply. } 22. a4 { This position has been seen in several correspondence games, all of them ending in a draw. } 22... Nb4 { A good way to get out of the pin. } 23. Qd2 Qf5 { This position is fine for Black. Our pieces are active and well placed. The b2-pawn and the f3-knight are potential targets. } *

