f4 Re8 { This is the best square for the rook. } 15. h3 a6 16. Qd2 Rb8 { With a good position for Black. We’ve managed to exchange a pair of knights and ....b5 is coming next. The game 0-1 (49) Ilincic, Z (2450)-Yilmaz, M (2630) Valjevo 2018 continued } 17. Bh6 Bxh6 18. Qxh6 b5 { Time to push the pawn! } 19. axb5 axb5 20. b4 cxb4 21. Na2 b3 22. Nb4 Bf5 23. Qd2 Bc2 24. Nxc2 bxc2 25. Qxc2 Qb6 { The passed b-pawn gives Black an advantage. } *

