 at some point. } 17. b3 Ba6 { Activating the bishop. } 18. Qc2 Ne5 { Black had a good position in ½-½  (36) Karjakin,S (2753)-Vitiugov,N (2719) Chiva 2015. We’ve managed to exchange a knight and the a6-bishop is quite active. } *

