il our structure. } 19. Ne4 Qe5 20. Nxc5 Qxc5 21. Qxc6 Rac8 { The resulting ending is equal as the c4-pawn will fall. For example } 22. Qxc5 Rxc5 23. Rfc1 Rxc4 24. Rxc4 Bxc4 { . } *

