1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. e3 { The Colle System. White is building up the position slowly, and is going for a setup with Bd3, b3 and Bb2. This system is popular in blitz and rapid even among top players. Although it's not so ambitious, White develops all the pieces to good squares and gets a playable position. } 3... d5 ( { As much as I prefer to avoid symmetry, this seems more natural to me than } 3... c5 { . } ) 4. c4 c5 { Transposes to the previous chapter. } *

